pgTitle: List of Eurovision Song Contest winners

rows.text: Poupée de cire, poupée de son
Manuel de la Calva, Ramón Arcusa
Maria José de Cerato, Aniano Alcalde
Un banc, un arbre, une rue
Jean-Paul Furnémont, Angelo Crisci, Rosario Marino Atria
Fly on the Wings of Love

15 May Since 2004 the contest has included a televised semi-final. In 2004 this was held on the Wednesday before the final, and between 2005 and 2007 it was held on the Thursday of "Eurovision Week". Since 2008 two semi-finals have been held, on Tuesday and Thursday respectively.
24 May Since 2008 the contest has included two semi-finals, held on the Tuesday and Thursday before the final.
